Name: Average time from \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\ to \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time between \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\ and \Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\ to \Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE\ for re-submission
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Minimun time from \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\ to next \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time it takes for a declaration to be \REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\ after being \APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time declarations spend in the process after being \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time until \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\ is overturned or followed by \Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Time from \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\ to \Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR\ in successful cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimun resolution time of cases after \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time for a declaration to be re-submitted after being \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for all activities to be completed after \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to \Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE\ after \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time it takes \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\ to be followed by any approval activity
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'", 'end': "activity == 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' or activity == 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'", 'aggregation': 'total'}

Name: Average time between \Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION\ and \Request Payment\ in cases where payment is eventually requested
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'
